      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1800 - Muhammad ibn Muslim and Zurara ibn A‘yan asked Abu Ja‘far Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) about fasting on the Day of Ashura.\nImam (as) said: \"Its fasting was practiced before the Month of Ramadan, but when the Month of Ramadan was prescribed, it was abandoned.\""
        ]
